description: If your tummy is rumbling for something yummy in Raleigh, Rum Cake Grande’ is the truck for you. C. Jay Johnson began baking rum cakes as a hobby 15 years ago, pleasing everyone with his gourmet family recipes. Now he’s making his dream of sharing these delicious desserts with the world come true with every new rum cake he bakes. Coffee rum cake, pineapple rum cake, Coconut, Chocolate, and Orange too- these are just a few that you’ll find on his colossal menu. Come on and take a taste of Raleigh’s favorite rum cake, you’ll surely savor every crumb.
name: Rum Cake Grande'
